Sabu Dastagir https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sabu_Dastagir 0 Sabu Dastagir (born Selar Sabu; 27 January 1924 – 2 December 1963) was an Indian film actor who later gained United States citizenship. He was normally credited only by his first name, Sabu, and is primarily known for his work in films during the 1930s–1940s in Britain and America. He was inducted into the Hollywood Walk of Fame in 1960. Sabu_Dastagir ( born Selar_Sabu ; 27_January_1924 – 2_December_1963 ) was an_Indian_film_actor who later gained United_States_citizenship .
